        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】GlocalMe UniCord 3 合 1 多功能 USB 线，，65W 快充 + 可 4G 上网 + 支援 Lightning</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/10/glocalme-unicord/parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=glocalme-unicord</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/10/glocalme-unicord/parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Glocalme]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GloCalMe UniCord]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286323</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>随著科技日新月异的发展，充电线早已不只是连接装置与电源的工具。GlocalMe 推出的 UniCord 被誉为全球首款 3 合 1 多功能 USB 充电线，支援 65W 快速充电，更可使用 4G Cloud SIM 为你连接网络，其重量仅为 44g。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286327" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011020836-694x377.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011020836-694x377.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011020836.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援 65W</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286331" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲使用 CloudSIM 技术，支援全球 4G 上网</p><p>UniCord 的最大卖点在于其独具匠心的 3 合 1 设计。它能使用 USB-C、Lightning 和 USB-A ，兼容市面上绝大多数电子装置。无论是智能手机、平板电脑、蓝牙耳机，还是其他配件，UniCord 都能为用户提供稳定且高效的充电与数据传输服务，消除了携带多条充电线的困扰，让出行更加便捷。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286330" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原生支援 USBC，使用转接头即可支援 Apple Lightning 及 USB-A</p><p>UniCord 因其出色的创新性和实用性，成功荣获在 CES 2025 展会 Android Authority 的「突破奖」，象征著它在充电线市场中开创了全新的方向。从设计上来看，UniCord 支援快速充电，亦可使用 Cloud SIM 连接 4G 网络，一条线就可充电、连接网络，大大提升了专业人士在创作和工作的便利。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286328" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021232-694x376.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021232-694x376.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021232.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286329" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021227-694x383.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="383" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021227-694x383.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021227.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104528-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104528-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104528.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104530-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104530-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104530.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>据官方网站数据显示，GloCalMe UniCord 售价为 29.99 美元（约港币 233.37 元），购买时可获赠送全球 1GB 90 日数据服务，价值 29 美元（约港币 225.66 元）。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://www.glocalme.com/product/unicord/?gad_source=1&amp;gclid=CjwKCAiAhP67BhAVEiwA2E_9g8wiUbSgdGBCPjA5nIlWA_kxw5D5c4r8r0bjXQGLfS_j186eyPmnehoC7jEQAvD_BwE">GlocalMe</a>、Unwire.hk</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
